49
00:04:53,839 --> 00:04:54,399
[SPEAKER_00] Dva i devet.

50
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,600
[SPEAKER_00] Dva i devet, u redu.

51
00:04:55,839 --> 00:04:57,199
