112
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:18,799
[SPEAKER_00] To je poput git tower.

113
00:11:18,879 --> 00:11:22,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ali došla je s gitom do nedavno, mislim.

114
00:11:22,399 --> 00:11:22,879
[SPEAKER_00] O, wow.

115
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,240
[SPEAKER_00] I stvarno je loše.

116
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:35,919
