1339
01:59:45,520 --> 01:59:50,399
[SPEAKER_01] Jer vrata za buku su, znate, čujete lošu jednu i ona vas uništava zauvijek.

1340
01:59:50,560 --> 01:59:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda mislite: U redu, nikad neću to učiniti.

1341
01:59:52,079 --> 01:59:52,640
[SPEAKER_01] Ne mogu.

1342
01:59:52,720 --> 01:59:52,800
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1343
